# Info

Invoked to generate data files dynamically. This can be used to create JSON data files programmatically.

# Example

```js
ServerEvents.generateData('kubejs:my_data', event => {
	// Generate custom data files
	event.json('my_data/custom.json', {
		key: 'value',
		numbers: [1, 2, 3]
	})
})
```
